	      	</p>
	    </div>
	    <hr/>
            <div>
            <h3>Potato</h3>
	      	<p>
	      	    <img style="height: 25%; margin-bottom: 10px" src="https://hl-grocery-prod-master.imgix.net/products/e0708a0e86461f70a298d4610b3b4bbdb685fa75?fill=solid&fit=fill&fm=jpg&h=256&pad=7&q=92&trim=auto&trim-md=0&w=256" />
	      	</p>
	    </div>
      </classification-target>
    </crowd-classifier>
  </div>